### ============================================
### RECOMMENDED: ASSIGN STUDENT TO CLASS (REST-compliant)
### ============================================

### Assign Student to Class (PATCH - Recommended)
PATCH https://localhost:5001/api/v1/students/S001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "schoolClassId": 1
}

### Unassign Student from Class (PATCH - Recommended)
PATCH https://localhost:5001/api/v1/students/S001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "schoolClassId": null
}

